PRIVACY POLICY
Last Updated: 24-07-2023
We take your privacy seriously and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our app that generates voice messages using AI technology (Clony).
I. INFORMATION WE COLLECT
We collect information you provide directly to us, such as your voice input and any personal information you provide when setting up an account, such as your name and email address. We also automatically collect certain information about your device, including: Device Information: We collect information about the device you use to access the App, including the device type, operating system, and mobile network information. Log Information: We automatically collect certain information about your use of the App, including the date and time you access the App, the features you use, and any errors that occur. Analytics Information: We use third-party analytics tools to collect information about how you use the App. This may include information about the pages you visit and how long you spend on each page. Uploaded audio files and audio data recorded in the app may be shared with our voice generation AI providers.
II. HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION
We use the information we collect to: Provide and improve the App; Communicate with you about the App, including updates and offers; Respond to your inquiries and requests; Analyze how the App is being used and identify trends and usage patterns; Detect and prevent fraud and other illegal activities.
III. HOW WE SHARE YOUR INFORMATION
We may share your information with third-party service providers who perform services on our behalf, such as hosting, data analysis, customer service, and marketing. These service providers may have access to your information only to perform these tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose. We may also share your information: With our affiliates, subsidiaries, and other related companies; In response to a subpoena, court order, or other legal request; To investigate, prevent, or take action regarding illegal activities, suspected fraud, or situations involving potential threats to the safety of any person; If we are acquired by or merged with another company, in which case your information may be transferred to the acquiring company.
IV. YOUR CHOICES
If you want to get all user related data deleted, please contact us at contact@clony.app.
V. SECURITY
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
VI. CHANGES TO THIS POLICY
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make material changes to this policy, we will notify you by email or through the App. Your continued use of the App after any changes to this policy will signify your acceptance of the changes.
VII. CONTACT US
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at contact@clony.app.